    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! It honestly breaks my heart a little to list my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for this beauty to find a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this one\u2014it\u2019s been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and has honestly barely seen a raindrop. It still has that 'new car' magic, and while there might be a tiny, invisible mark from a stray pebble on a Sunday cruise, you\u2019d have to look incredibly hard to find it. It drives like a dream and looks even better. Swing by, let's grab a coffee, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented in showroom-grade condition, this S54-powered icon is a masterclass in analog precision. The engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, with the critical VANOS and rod bearing services already performed to exceed OEM specs. Featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a bespoke suspension setup tuned for zero-lash turn-in, the chassis dynamics are sharper than the day it left Regensburg. The paint depth is remarkable, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that highlights the iconic body lines. This is a turn-key collector piece for the enthusiast who demands peak mechanical integrity and uncompromised performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom floor quality. Zero flaws. Smells new. Not a single scratch. Fastest sale in the city.",
      "price": 43500.0,
