    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a living legacy. This automotive masterpiece is less a vehicle and more a time capsule, preserved with a devotion that borders on the sacred. Its silhouette cuts through the air with a timeless grace, while the paintwork possesses a depth and luster that captures the very essence of the golden hour. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury, echoing an era of uncompromising craftsmanship where every touchpoint tells a story of elegance. To drive this car is to command a symphony of engineering, a soul-stirring experience that turns every mundane errand into a grand tour. This is an invitation to become the next curator of a truly peerless specimen, a rare jewel polished to perfection and waiting for its next great adventure.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
